  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seek trough the nature around, find all ingredients for a cozy cup of camping coffee!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short game, remarkable feeling:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gorgeous alive green nature</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The beautiful bond of the characters through different seasons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The smell of 5 different coffees</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The cozines of a campfire. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carefully handrawed just for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965730/extras/7931facd6c20cd2150bbd3ac805eafc9.avif?t=1739504229\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965730/extras_big/7931facd6c20cd2150bbd3ac805eafc9.avif?t=1739504229 width=800 height=476 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965730/extras/f41ef3399f25cd880c62dbe6f9db95b8.poster.avif?t=1739504229\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965730/extras/f41ef3399f25cd880c62dbe6f9db95b8.webm?t=1739504229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965730/extras/f41ef3399f25cd880c62dbe6f9db95b8.mp4?t=1739504229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965730/extras/6230f434e4eb1d39c0ad8d331bd1d494.poster.avif?t=1739504229\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965730/extras/6230f434e4eb1d39c0ad8d331bd1d494.webm?t=1739504229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2965730/extras/6230f434e4eb1d39c0ad8d331bd1d494.mp4?t=1739504229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A game about searching in the fields around a camp, to find the ingredients and make a delightful coffee recipe. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Everyone has their own way of preparing and enjoying a cozy camping coffee, with nature around, and a bonfire nearby.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Discover the recipes, the characters, and the diffrent stories about cozy camping coffees.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    To do so, you’ll need to find all the ingredients, cutlery, and even the material to build a campfire!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Can you prepare all the coffee recipes?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    - Find out where the ingredients are hidden. [80+ objects]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    - Collect them all, and make delicious coffee.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    - Explore a live and colorful scene carefully hand drawn for you.</p>",
